cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper deals with image recognition and annotation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The use of mixture models and Fisher Vectors also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper mentions achieving state-of-the-art results for image search by a sentence, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or natural language processing (cs.CL).
